<h1 data-start="4264" data-end="4292">NEXT STEP (Very Important)</h1>
<p data-start="4293" data-end="4355">In the next step we will detect <strong data-start="4325" data-end="4349">suspicious processes</strong> like:</p>
<ul data-start="4356" data-end="4405">
<li data-start="4356" data-end="4372">
<p data-start="4358" data-end="4372">powershell.exe</p>
</li>
<li data-start="4373" data-end="4382">
<p data-start="4375" data-end="4382">cmd.exe</p>
</li>
<li data-start="4383" data-end="4395">
<p data-start="4385" data-end="4395">whoami.exe</p>
</li>
<li data-start="4396" data-end="4405">
<p data-start="4398" data-end="4405">net.exe</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="4407" data-end="4460">This is where the <strong data-start="4425" data-end="4445">attack detection</strong> really starts.</p>
