<p data-start="37" data-end="212">It means <strong data-start="46" data-end="91">Windows Security logs are reaching Splunk</strong>, and <strong data-start="97" data-end="125">Event ID 4688 does exist</strong> in your data. So the earlier <code data-start="155" data-end="165">0 events</code> result was most likely caused by one of these:</p>
<ul data-start="214" data-end="314">
<li data-start="214" data-end="236">
<p data-start="216" data-end="236">wrong <strong data-start="222" data-end="236">time range</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="237" data-end="257">
