</li>
<li data-start="258" data-end="286">
<p data-start="260" data-end="286">host/index filtering issue</p>
</li>
<li data-start="287" data-end="314">
<p data-start="289" data-end="314">temporary search mismatch</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="316" data-end="356">This is actually a very good SOC lesson:</p>
<blockquote data-start="357" data-end="468">
<p data-start="359" data-end="468">sometimes the data exists, but the first search does not reveal it because of search scope or time selection.</p>
</blockquote>
<p data-start="470" data-end="498">So now we continue properly.</p>
<hr data-start="500" data-end="503">
<h1 data-start="505" data-end="528">PROJECT 3 — STAGE 3</h1>
