<hr data-start="2774" data-end="2777">
<h2 data-start="2779" data-end="2806">2. WHAT THIS SEARCH DOES</h2>
<p data-start="2808" data-end="2825">This search asks:</p>
<blockquote data-start="2827" data-end="2898">
<p data-start="2829" data-end="2898">“Show me only Windows Security logs where a new process was created.”</p>
</blockquote>
<p data-start="2900" data-end="3012">So now we are no longer looking at all security events.<br data-start="2955" data-end="2958">
We are focusing only on <strong data-start="2982" data-end="3011">process creation activity</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="3014" data-end="3017">
<h2 data-start="3019" data-end="3047">3. WHAT YOU SHOULD EXPECT</h2>
<p data-start="3049" data-end="3064">You should see:</p>
<ul data-start="3065" data-end="3151">
<li data-start="3065" data-end="3087">
<p data-start="3067" data-end="3087">multiple 4688 events</p>
</li>
<li data-start="3088" data-end="3105">
<p data-start="3090" data-end="3105">different hosts</p>
</li>
<li data-start="3106" data-end="3123">
<p data-start="3108" data-end="3123">different users</p>
</li>
<li data-start="3124" data-end="3151">
<p data-start="3126" data-end="3151">process execution records</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="3153" data-end="3198">You may also begin to see useful fields like:</p>
<ul data-start="3199" data-end="3292">
<li data-start="3199" data-end="3219">
<p data-start="3201" data-end="3219"><code data-start="3201" data-end="3219">New_Process_Name</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="3220" data-end="3243">
<p data-start="3222" data-end="3243"><code data-start="3222" data-end="3243">Parent_Process_Name</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="3244" data-end="3259">
<p data-start="3246" data-end="3259"><code data-start="3246" data-end="3259">CommandLine</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="3260" data-end="3279">
<p data-start="3262" data-end="3279"><code data-start="3262" data-end="3279">SubjectUserName</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="3280" data-end="3292">
<p data-start="3282" data-end="3292"><code data-start="3282" data-end="3292">Computer</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="3294" data-end="3373">Not every field will always appear the same way, but we will inspect that next.</p>
