<p data-start="3653" data-end="3682">A SOC analyst first confirms:</p>
<ul data-start="3683" data-end="3783">
<li data-start="3683" data-end="3705">
<p data-start="3685" data-end="3705">does the data exist?</p>
</li>
<li data-start="3706" data-end="3744">
<p data-start="3708" data-end="3744">can I isolate the event type I need?</p>
</li>
<li data-start="3745" data-end="3783">
<p data-start="3747" data-end="3783">can I build detection logic from it?</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="3785" data-end="3845">By filtering directly to 4688, we are preparing to identify:</p>
<ul data-start="3846" data-end="3943">
<li data-start="3846" data-end="3867">
<p data-start="3848" data-end="3867">suspicious commands</p>
</li>
<li data-start="3868" data-end="3886">
<p data-start="3870" data-end="3886">suspicious tools</p>
</li>
<li data-start="3887" data-end="3913">
<p data-start="3889" data-end="3913">suspicious user activity</p>
</li>
<li data-start="3914" data-end="3943">
<p data-start="3916" data-end="3943">suspicious execution chains</p>
</li>
</ul>
