<p data-start="61" data-end="202">So the problem is not that 4688 is missing.<br data-start="104" data-end="107">
The problem is that <strong data-start="127" data-end="201">Splunk is not extracting the field in a way your direct filter can use</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="204" data-end="234">We now do the next exact step.</p>
