<h2 data-start="40" data-end="69">What the screenshot proves</h2>
<p data-start="70" data-end="117">This is a real <strong data-start="85" data-end="116">4688 process creation event</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="119" data-end="146">From the raw log I can see:</p>
<ul data-start="147" data-end="325">
